<br>
A non-primal warrior at high 60s is probably around 2.4 on &quot;normal&quot; mobs and ~1.3 on Luclin mega AC bosses, but that's a guess <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  .  c really depends strongly on your atk and the AC of the kind of mobs you're fighting.<br>
<br>
